# Force LF for the shell scripts and zsh configs so they run/parse on Linux
# regardless of core.autocrlf on the committer's machine. Applies repo-wide,
# covering every project folder (Power_Ubuntu, Power_Hacker, ...). my_p10k.zsh is
# served raw from GitHub and sourced by zsh, so it must be LF too or the prompt
# inherits stray carriage returns.
*.sh   text eol=lf
*.zsh  text eol=lf
